@page "/topics"

<PageTitle>Topics</PageTitle>

<div class="space-y-6">
    <header class="space-y-3">
        <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-signal-600">Cutover</p>
            <h1 class="font-display text-4xl text-cinder-950 sm:text-5xl">Legacy topics page retired</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="max-w-5xl text-base leading-8 text-cinder-800">
            Server-rendered server-profile management, topic probing, preset editing, and live subscription controls are
            being removed in favor of the browser-first client, API preferences, and realtime broker flow.
        </p>
    </header>

    <section class="grid gap-4 xl:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr]">
        <article class="liquid-panel rounded-[1.6rem] p-6">
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-cinder-950">Removed from the server page</h2>
            <ul class="mt-5 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-cinder-800/84">
                <li>Active server switching and broker profile editing.</li>
                <li>Live MQTT topic probing and immediate subscribe or unsubscribe actions.</li>
                <li>Preset and topic-discovery flows tied to the legacy server runtime.</li>
            </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="liquid-panel rounded-[1.6rem] p-6">
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-cinder-950">Cutover status</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-cinder-800/82">
                This route remains only as a migration marker while the final server-rendered detail pages are removed.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <a href="/" class="liquid-button inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/messages" class="liquid-button inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Messages</a>
                <a href="/settings" class="liquid-button inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Settings</a>
            </div>
        </article>
    </section>
</div>
